-- // Effects form a join-semilattice:  Pure ⊑ {IO, Async, State, Except} ⊑ Combined.
-- // `combineEffects` computes the join.  The codegen maps each effect to a Lean 4
-- // monad transformer stack (StateT / ExceptT / IO).
